for table in table_id:
    query = """
    SELECT *
    FROM `{}.{}`
    """.format(dataset_id, table)

    df = client.query(query).to_dataframe()

    print("Tabla: {}".format(table))
    print("-------------------------")

df1.MarkDown1 = df1.MarkDown1.replace('NA', 0).astype(float)
df1.MarkDown2 = df1.MarkDown2.replace('NA', 0).astype(float)
df1.MarkDown3 = df1.MarkDown3.replace('NA', 0).astype(float)
df1.MarkDown4 = df1.MarkDown4.replace('NA', 0).astype(float)
df1.MarkDown5 = df1.MarkDown5.replace('NA', 0).astype(float)
df1.IsHoliday = df1.IsHoliday.apply(lambda x: 0 if x == False else 1)
df1.Dept = df1.Dept.astype('category').cat.codes
df1.Store = df1.Store.astype('category').cat.codes
df1.Type = df1.Type.astype('category').cat.codes
df1.Unemployment = df1.Unemployment.astype(float)
df1.CPI = df1.CPI.astype(float)
df1.Date = pd.to_datetime(df1.Date)
